steps.name: Given I am logged in with "sudip_pudasaini@hotmail.com" and password "assessmentqa"
And I land on my tasks page
When I click on manage subtasks button
And enter text "This is the sub-task with special chars: @#$@#123" on subtask description

Then I subtask counter "2" on manage subtask button should be increased
